Create a translator app that enables English and Spanish speakers to communicate

Refinement 1:
  Translate a question spoken in English to Spanish speech
  Translate an answer spoken in Spanish to English speech

Refinement 2:
  1.  Prompt for a question in English and record into an audio file
  2.  Transcribe audio file into English text
  3.  Translate English text in Spanish text
  4.  Synthesize Spanish text into Spanish audio
  5.  Play Spanish audio

  6.  Prompt for an answer in Spanish and record into an audio file
  7.  Transcribe Spanish audio into Spanish text
  8.  Translate Spanish text into English text
  9.  Synthesize English text into English audio
  10. Play English audio
